525
00:44:00,150 --> 00:44:05,460
♫ All are just illusions ♫

526
00:44:06,290 --> 00:44:11,800
♫ During the cold night, my yearning for you runs as a river ♫

527
00:44:11,800 --> 00:44:17,070
